### TikTok Live Backend API
### Base URL — change to your deployed host if not running locally
@host = https://tiktok-app-4ahgj.ondigitalocean.app


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTH — Login (cookie-based, for browser use)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Login as admin
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "banana",
  "password": "almost-machine-actress"
}

### Check auth status (needs session cookie from login)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/status

### Logout
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### API TOKENS — Universal auth (no cookies needed)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create an API token (admin only — login first, then use cookie)
### The response will return the raw token. Copy it to @token below.
# @name createToken
POST {{host}}/api/admin/tokens
Content-Type: application/json
X-CSRF-Token: {{login.response.body.csrfToken}}
Cookie: session_id={{login.response.headers.Set-Cookie}}

{
  "username": "banana",
  "name": "shared-api-token",
  "expireDays": 30
}

### ─── Paste your API token here ──────────────────────────────────────────
@token = wobKh3kzdsQ-EPtsd8zdG_HVVJmZ5W30QDyOv0KqCthGFAZZ0zvvMiuDPDR1RrDt


### List all API tokens (admin)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Revoke a token (admin) — replace TOKEN_ID
# DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/tokens/TOKEN_ID
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### TIKTOK — Profile lookup (auth required)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get TikTok profile by handle
GET {{host}}/api/tiktok/profile/@tiktok
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

